    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers straightforward transportation at an accessible price. It shows its age cosmetically and is best suited for a buyer who values practicality and value over perfection, but it still presents a solid opportunity for basic daily use, a second vehicle, or a project. Priced to sell and represented honestly, this is a sensible way to get into a vehicle without overspending.",
