    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right person? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport or a solid little project. Honest car, straightforward value, and priced to make sense for what it is. If you\u2019re after something cheap, practical, and worth a look, this could be the one.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget driver with a strong-running engine, responsive automatic transmission, and a chassis that still feels planted where it counts. Not a showpiece, but it has honest bones, good mechanical character, and the kind of straightforward platform that rewards a hands-on owner. A great opportunity for someone who wants affordable entry into a dependable, usable car with room to sort cosmetics and small items over time.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
