      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of road-worn personality you can\u2019t fake\u2014a faithful old machine with presence, charm, and plenty of story left to write. It starts conversations before it even leaves the driveway, and for the right buyer, it\u2019s a budget-friendly way into something with real character. Whether you want a practical runaround, a hands-on project, or simply a vehicle with a little soul, this one offers an opportunity to make it your own without spending a fortune.",
